  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Holy Road, you play the role of an exiled bishop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To reobtain what was rightfully yours, you must start all over from the very beginning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must start your kingdom, increase its population while defending your citizens, and thus increasing your wealth and power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only by doing this will you be able to get revenge on those that wronged you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to build your kingdom from scratch?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find out for yourself in this kingdom-building simulation game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Kingdom Building Simulation Experience</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct Buildings</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase your Population</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend your Citizens</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Amass Wealth and Power</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And Defeat your Enemies!</p></li></ul></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Holy Road, you play the role of an exiled bishop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To reobtain what was rightfully yours, you must start all over from the very beginning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must start your kingdom, increase its population while defending your citizens, and thus increasing your wealth and power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only by doing this will you be able to get revenge on those that wronged you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to build your kingdom from scratch?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find out for yourself in this kingdom-building simulation game!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Kingdom Building Simulation Experience</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct Buildings</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase your Population</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend your Citizens</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Amass Wealth and Power</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And Defeat your Enemies!</p></li></ul></p></li></ul>",
